      <title>国际清算银行称财政债务狂潮是全球最大的稳定威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/fiscal-debt-binge-is-world-s-biggest-stability-threat-bis-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际清算银行表示，政府借贷习惯对世界经济稳定构成了最大威胁，近期市场情绪的变化应该起到警示作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/fiscal-debt-binge-is-world-s-biggest-stability-threat-bis-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法院裁定赞比亚前总统伦古无资格连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/court-finds-zambia-ex-president-lungu-ineligible-for-re-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚法院裁定，前总统埃德加·伦古不能参加未来的国家最高职位选举，因为他已经担任过两次国家最高职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/court-finds-zambia-ex-president-lungu-ineligible-for-re-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 11:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚表明中东不能将稳定视为理所当然</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/syria-shows-how-middle-east-can-t-take-stability-for-granted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当这位国际货币基金组织总裁上个月访问开罗时，她发现自己正盯着一幅巨大的编织挂图，埃及的地图错综复杂，这或许是她在阿拉伯世界所承担的微妙任务的一个隐喻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/syria-shows-how-middle-east-can-t-take-stability-for-granted</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选后美国小企业乐观情绪飙升至三年来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/us-small-business-optimism-soars-to-three-year-high-after-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普确定重返白宫后，由于预期将出台更多有利的经济政策，美国小企业乐观情绪在 11 月份飙升至三年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/us-small-business-optimism-soars-to-three-year-high-after-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡成为首位在贪污案审判中作证的以色列总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/netanyahu-takes-the-witness-stand-in-historic-corruption-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡首次在腐败案审判中出庭作证，他被指控犯有贿赂、欺诈和背信弃义等罪名，此案近十年来一直严重扰乱以色列的政治生活。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/netanyahu-takes-the-witness-stand-in-historic-corruption-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:35:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
